Members of Eksteen Ryu Bushido Freestyle Karate do and Mixed Martial Arts (MMA) Institute participated in the recent Gauteng All Styles Dennis Pandaram Martial Arts Invitational Challenge winning 12 podium places in the process.
The eight warriors representing Limpopo brought back two gold, five silver and five bronze medals in their respective categories. They are Mundus Uys, Letladi Makgoba, Mpho Chokolo, Ayo Manganyi, Katlego Mongoai, Ofentse Ledwaba, Sebego Mashego and Makhudu Mokobane.
Story: RC Myburgh
